<br><br><font color="004fd2" face="arial" size="6"><b>If your desire is to be average, then apply for a "job" with our competitors. However, if your desire is to be GREAT, and work for a company that actually cares about their employees - then start a "career" as a Security Professional with our TEAM!</b><br></font><font color="00000" face="arial" size="3"><br>Transcend Security Solutions, a Leading Contract Security Services Provider, is in IMMEDIATE need of highly qualified Security Professionals to fill Full-Time, Part-Time, and Flex positions for the Greater Phoenix area! <b> NOTE:</b> This Job Posting is long because we want to be as transparent with you as we can. We want you to know that you will NOT get blindsided once you join the Best-in-Class Security Provider in Arizona!</font><br>
<br><font color="00000" face="arial" size="3">We sound like a broken record but it's true, Transcend Security has experienced AMAZING growth. And because of this growth we MUST fill multiple shifts at various locations. Possessing a current, valid Arizona DPS-issued Guard Card is a plus, but not a requirement.<b> If you currently do not have an Arizona Guard Card License, Transcend Security can help you out.</b> A commanding presence is a MUST. New members of our team will provide security services to a wide variety of residential communities and commercial properties across the Valley. In addition, a commanding presence and strong customer service skills are a MUST.</font><br>
<br><font color="004fd2" face="arial" size="3"><b>NOTE:</font><font color="00000" face="arial" size="3"> FIRST &amp; FOREMOST</b> - To apply, applicants <b>MUST CLICK</b> on the Transcend Security logo at this bottom of this page to enter the Transcend Security Application &amp; Assessment Center. Submissions made through the Assessment Center will be reviewed and acted upon first. If you do not have access to a PC to take the Assessment, please reply to this posting with your resume.</font>
<br><br><br><font color="004fd2" face="arial" size="4"><b>Why Join the Transcend Security Team?</b></font>
<ul><li type="circle"><font color="00000" face="arial" size="3"><b>Free Security Uniforms &amp; Equipment! </b> - You Pay Nothing &amp; No Deposit Taken! Seriously, some of our competitors will charge LARGE deposits upfront (that you never truly get back); some will take a portion of your hard-earned money each pay period; and some will even FORCE you to buy your own uniforms, equipment, and/or gear, but NOT at Transcend! Again, you pay nothing &amp; no deposit is taken!</font><br><br>
<li type="circle"><font color="00000" face="arial" size="3"><b>You'll Get Paid ON-TIME &amp; Your Paycheck WON'T Bounce!</b> - Believe it or not (and as many of you are aware), this is a problem with some of our competitors, but NOT at Transcend!</font><br><br>
<li type="circle"><font color="00000" face="arial" size="3"><b>Company Paid Sick Time!</b> - No other Security Company provides this benefit!</font><br><br>
<li type="circle"><font color="00000" face="arial" size="3"><b>True Vacation Pay!</b> - To some of our competitors, the offering of "vacation pay" is just simply a bonus program, disguised as vacation pay, when it really isn't. And the amount of vacation time increases as your time with Transcend increases. </font><br><br>
<li type="circle"><font color="00000" face="arial" size="3"><b>Free Life Insurance Policy!</b> - Transcend Security provides all full-time hourly (that regularly work 30 hours or more) and salaried team members a $10,000.00 Life Insurance Policy at NO CHARGE!</font><br><br>
<li type="circle"><font color="00000" face="arial" size="3"><b>Medical, Dental and Vision Benefits!</b> - Medical, Dental and Vision Benefits are available to full-time hourly (that regularly work 30 hours or more) and salaried team members, and their families.</font><br><br>
<li type="circle"><font color="00000" face="arial" size="3"><b>No Charge for Guard Card Classes!</b> - A Guard Card License is $72.00, and it's paid directly to the Arizona Department of Public Safety. If a company asks you to pay more than that, ask them why? Then, contact the Department of Public Safety IMMEDIATELY!</font><br><br></ul>
<font color="004fd2" face="arial" size="4"><b>Summary</b></font><br>
<br><font color="00000" face="arial" size="3">Headquartered in Scottsdale, Arizona (with offices in Tucson), <b><font color="004fd2">Transcend Security Solutions</font></b> is Arizona's fastest growing private security firm, and one of only a few premier providers of highly trained security professionals to a variety of vertical markets. Transcend Security delivers superior physical and virtual security services that protect people, homes and businesses. Our Mission Statement guides us:<br>
<br>
 <font size="3"><b><font color="004fd2"><i>"To provide a level of service that transcends good work, and discovers the tremendous experience of doing great work."</font></b></i><br>
<br>
</font><font color="00000" face="arial" size="3">So if you're ready for a career with the most officer-friendly security firm in Arizona, we would love to have you join our team!<br>
<br>
<br>
<font color="004fd2" face="arial" size="4"><b>General Accountabilities:</font></b><br>
<br>
<ul><li type="circle"><font color="00000" face="arial" size="3">An extremely high-level of customer service skills are needed.</font><br>
<li type="circle"><font color="00000" face="arial" size="3">Routine heavy lifting may be required.</font><br>
<li type="circle"><font color="00000" face="arial" size="3">Routine walking is required.</font><br>
<li type="circle"><font color="00000" face="arial" size="3">Climbing Staircases multiple times throughout shift may be required.</font><br>
<li type="circle"><font color="00000" face="arial" size="3">Monitor and authorize entrance and departure of residents, visitors, and other persons, in order to maintain security of the entirety of the building.</font><br>
<li type="circle"><font color="00000" face="arial" size="3">Ensure a welcoming and comfortable atmosphere.</font><br>
<li type="circle"><font color="00000" face="arial" size="3">Knowledgeable about residential and/or commercial rules, and effectively answer inquiries specific to the property.</font><br>
<li type="circle"><font color="00000" face="arial" size="3">Watch for irregular or unusual conditions that may create security concerns or safety hazards.</font><br>
<li type="circle"><font color="00000" face="arial" size="3">Affectively understand and utilize technology products such as a smartphone, computer, tablet, etc.</font><br>
<li type="circle"><font color="00000" face="arial" size="3">Ability to prepare reports in a clear and concise manner.</font><br>
<li type="circle"><font color="00000" face="arial" size="3">Spelling and grammar skills are essential.</font><br>
<li type="circle"><font color="00000" face="arial" size="3">Provide assistance to residents, guests, tenants, visitors, and other persons in a courteous and professional manner.</font><br>
<li type="circle"><font color="00000" face="arial" size="3">Answer alarms and investigate disturbances.</font><br>
<li type="circle"><font color="00000" face="arial" size="3">The company reserves the right to add or change duties at any time.</font><br></ul>
<br>
<br><font color="004fd2" face="arial" size="4"><b>Job Qualifications &amp; Requirements:</font></b><br><br>
<ul><li type="circle"><font color="00000" face="arial" size="3">GREAT Attitude and Team Spirit is required.</font><br>
<li type="circle"><font color="00000" face="arial" size="3">Willingness to provide a level of service that is unmatched.</font><br>
<li type="circle"><font color="00000" face="arial" size="3">Must be at least age 18.</font><br>
<li type="circle"><font color="00000" face="arial" size="3">Must be able to pass an in-depth criminal background check.</font><br>
<li type="circle"><font color="00000" face="arial" size="3">Must be able to pass a drug screening. (This is a zero tolerance work environment).</font><br>
<li type="circle"><font color="00000" face="arial" size="3">Must have a reliable means of transportation.</font><br>
<li type="circle"><font color="00000" face="arial" size="3">Must have the legal right to work in the United States.</font><br>
<li type="circle"><font color="00000" face="arial" size="3">Must have the ability to effectively speak, read, and write English.</font><br>
<li type="circle"><font color="00000" face="arial" size="3">Ability to pass an English composition assessment upon request (This ensures the ability to utilize proper grammar &amp; spelling for report writing).</font><br>
<li type="circle"><font color="00000" face="arial" size="3">Must have a High School Diploma or Equivalent.</font></ul><br>
<br><font color="004fd2" face="arial" size="4"><b>Skills:</font></b><br><br>
<ul>
<li type="circle"><font color="00000" face="arial" size="3">Possess a high level of customer service skills.</font><br>
<li type="circle"><font color="00000" face="arial" size="3">Active listening skills.</font><br>
<li type="circle"><font color="00000" face="arial" size="3">Ability to assess and evaluate situations quickly and effectively.</font><br>
<li type="circle"><font color="00000" face="arial" size="3">Ability to identify critical issues quickly and accurately.</font><br>
<li type="circle"><font color="00000" face="arial" size="3">Attention to detail.</font><br>
<li type="circle"><font color="00000" face="arial" size="3">Interpersonal and communication skills.</font><br>
<li type="circle"><font color="00000" face="arial" size="3">Technologically savvy.</font><br>
<li type="circle"><font color="00000" face="arial" size="3">Ability to write clear and concise electronic reports.</font><br>
<li type="circle"><font color="00000" face="arial" size="3">Spelling and grammar skills are essential.</font><br>
<li type="circle"><font color="00000" face="arial" size="3">Emergency response capabilities.</font><br>
<br>
<br>
</font><font color="00000" face="arial" size="4">APPLY HERE - Click the</font><font color="004fd2" face="arial" size="4"><b> Transcend Security</b></font><font color="00000" face="arial" size="4"> logo below to be taken to the Transcend Security Application &amp; Assessment Center to apply.<br>
<br>
NOTE - The Application &amp; Assessment requires Adobe Flash Player to be viewed, so it is not accessible via Mobile Device. If you don't have Adobe Flash Player installed on your computer, you may download it from Adobe.com. In addition, a Mouse &amp; Keyboard are required to take some of the Assessments.<br>
<br>
<a href="http://www.ondemandassessment.com/verify/apply/BSARRqD/ChbCCPbE" rel="nofollow"><img src="http://static.wixstatic.com/media/1e0d1f_be7191ad244c433184e28262aff51e00.png_256" alt="Tranny 2.png"></a></font></font></li></li></li></li></li></li></li></li></li></li></ul></li></li></li></li></li></li></li></li></li></li></li></li></li></li></li></li></li></li></li></li></li></li></li></li></li></li></li></li></li></li></li>    </section>

